@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_smnlcm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.84)) * (0.22 / (v1 + 0.25 * v2 + 0.73)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.57) + 0.69)
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.16 * v2 + 0.39)) - ((tmp + 0.20 + v2 + 0.50) - v1))
    data[tid] = v0
